<refsect1 id="harfbuzz-hb-graphite2.description" role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>Functions for using HarfBuzz with fonts that include Graphite features.</para>
<para>For Graphite features to work, you must be sure that HarfBuzz was compiled
with the <literal>graphite2</literal> shaping engine enabled. Currently, the default is to
not enable <literal>graphite2</literal> shaping.</para>

</refsect1>
