<refsect2 id="hb-graphite2-face-get-gr-face" role="function" condition="since:0.9.10">
<title>hb_graphite2_face_get_gr_face&#160;()</title>
<indexterm zone="hb-graphite2-face-get-gr-face" role="0.9.10"><primary>hb_graphite2_face_get_gr_face</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting language="C"><link linkend="gr-face"><returnvalue>gr_face</returnvalue></link>&#160;*
hb_graphite2_face_get_gr_face (<parameter><link linkend="hb-face-t"><type>hb_face_t</type></link> *face</parameter>);</programlisting>
<para>Fetches the Graphite2 gr_face corresponding to the specified
<link linkend="hb-face-t"><type>hb_face_t</type></link> face object.</para>

